      <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-bold mb-4">Contents</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
        <a href="#what-is-flyweb" class="text-fw-muted hover:text-fw-mint transition-colors py-1">1. What is FlyWeb?</a>
